channel.title: SwiftPkz 317 Client V2 - IP CHANGER, CUSTOM SPRITES, MUSIC PLAYER
channel.description:
I've decided to release my 317 client open source. And I am not going to be working on my 317. So here it is.
Features -Working chatbox -Working redstones -Correctly alligned chat text with buttons[e.g. Public: Hide] -Working map -New RS gameframe[before the HD update] -All skillcapes -All god wars items -New HP bar [credits given at bottom] -Item, Object, and NPC ID lists -Working server and port changing buttons -Working JFrame -Open Source
Download*Links will be mirrored soon
Pictures High Detail, working chatbox, working red stones, working everything :]
Hunting Cape & Hood, there is also a trimmed.
HP Bar
Virus scans prove nothing as they cannot scan for malicious code, that when ran can cause harm to the computer. This client DOES NOT have malicious code, or botnets. So no need to worry.
